        <content><![CDATA[<p>In the <a href="%(link0)">page editor</a>, the element options (edit point&nbsp;<img style="width: 14px;" title="selectionIconActive" src="%(link1)" alt="" /> at the element) show a gear wheel (<img style="width: 14px;" title="propertyIconActive" src="%(link2)" alt="" />) that opens the element settings dialog.</p>]]></content>
