    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The dialog has various sections, not all present every time. The settings we talk about here, are the ones in the "Settings" section. These are the ones configured for the formatter. As you see, the developer can configure various widgets for those settings to ease the editors task.</p>
<p>Just for completeness, we provide an overview on the different sections of the settings dialog here:</p>]]></content>
